		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This has been happening to me frequently on one machine I use, using chrome in incognito mode. I do this so when all the private tabs close all he cookies and whatnot are cleared up. However, as long as I keep one private tab open, the session stays alive for the various sites I've logged into. Except here, where if I leave the forum I am almost certainly going to be logged out when I come back. Leaving a forum tab open seems to prevent this for some amount of time.

		

